    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-04-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-04-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="283"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d283">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Baker</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-04-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 17, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your failure to send full information in regard to Bluefields incident has been
                    embarrassing here. You should go there at once. No officer, of this Government
                    was authorized to participate with Nicaraguan authorities and British consul in
                    organizing provisional administration.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
